# Build artifacts
#
# `skill.wasm` and `Cargo.lock` are deliberately NOT ignored under templates/:
# published skills ship their compiled module in the bundle, and the templates
# match that convention so a fresh clone can run `./tools/validate templates`
# without a toolchain installed. CI rebuilds them from source before
# validating, so a source change that breaks the build still fails the run.
skills/*/target/
sdk/rust/target/
sdk/assemblyscript/node_modules/
sdk/assemblyscript/package-lock.json
templates/*/target/
templates/*/node_modules/
templates/*/package-lock.json
